WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 29]

01:16.080 --> 01:16.810
It's the curse.

01:18.310 --> 01:19.340
Have I not much time left?

01:44.390 --> 01:46.220
- My Lord! - My Lord.

01:46.670 --> 01:47.250
My Lord.

01:47.470 --> 01:48.060
My Lord!

01:51.310 --> 01:51.860
My Lord!

01:53.640 --> 01:54.620
My Lord, what's wrong?

01:56.270 --> 01:56.890
My Lord!

01:56.910 --> 01:57.370
Here.

02:08.600 --> 02:09.220
My Lord.

02:10.270 --> 02:10.890
What happened to him?

02:12.240 --> 02:12.970
Thousands of years ago,

02:13.670 --> 02:14.970
the Lord was cursed by an ancient god.

02:15.870 --> 02:17.370
If he doesn't absorb the Divine Tree's power,

02:17.760 --> 02:19.970
he'll suffer unspeakable torment

02:20.390 --> 02:22.020
and eventually go mad and die.

02:23.320 --> 02:24.500
Then let's attack Duanming City

02:24.760 --> 02:25.810
and bring the Divine Tree here!

02:26.110 --> 02:26.690
Stop!

02:28.760 --> 02:30.570
Wanxian Sect is guarding the mountain-sea barrier.

02:31.480 --> 02:32.850
With our current power,

02:32.870 --> 02:34.250
we can only enter alone.

02:34.830 --> 02:36.020
How can we

02:36.320 --> 02:37.620
take Duanming City and capture the Divine Tree

02:37.640 --> 02:38.620
single-handedly?

03:07.830 --> 03:08.900
What's that?

03:09.390 --> 03:10.180
Smells amazing.

03:10.870 --> 03:11.530
Give it a try?

03:11.920 --> 03:12.620
Let me help you up.

03:12.920 --> 03:13.500
No,

03:14.800 --> 03:15.810
I can get up on my own.

03:18.390 --> 03:19.060
Watch out!

03:19.640 --> 03:20.250
Look.

03:21.270 --> 03:21.900
Let me.

03:24.320 --> 03:24.850
Here.

03:27.360 --> 03:28.090
It's your fault.

03:28.360 --> 03:29.300
If you hadn't held me,

03:29.550 --> 03:30.740
I could've run over there.

03:31.040 --> 03:32.020
Okay. You're the strongest.

03:34.390 --> 03:36.250
I didn't say I was hungry. Why did you cook?

03:36.920 --> 03:38.130
Still have to eat.

03:38.390 --> 03:38.970
Fine.

03:39.830 --> 03:40.810
Since you made it,

03:41.550 --> 03:42.620
I'll have a little.

03:42.920 --> 03:43.460
Alright.

03:44.920 --> 03:47.020
Master, I'm sorry.

03:47.150 --> 03:48.500
I didn't cook for you more often.

03:49.080 --> 03:50.250
Then make it right.

03:55.240 --> 03:55.900
Master.

03:57.270 --> 03:59.060
I'm going to Duanming City with Tongzhou tomorrow.

04:07.270 --> 04:08.130
Why?

04:09.040 --> 04:10.130
Strange things keep happening in the East Sea.

04:10.710 --> 04:12.500
There've been heavy casualties near Duanming City.

04:13.110 --> 04:14.500
The Sea Calamity might come early.

04:14.990 --> 04:17.410
Master, you know I can't avoid it.

04:17.920 --> 04:19.900
Why can't you?

04:20.230 --> 04:21.860
There are so many people in this world.

04:22.270 --> 04:23.370
What difference does one more make?

04:24.440 --> 04:26.740
And what difference does one less make?

04:29.640 --> 04:30.370
Master.

04:33.120 --> 04:35.420
Back then, Qingcheng

04:36.080 --> 04:38.770
was brilliant beyond compare.

04:39.910 --> 04:40.660
And what happened to him?

04:41.710 --> 04:42.300
He died.

04:45.590 --> 04:46.740
Dead!

04:54.080 --> 04:55.060
He's gone,

04:55.390 --> 04:56.250
and we're all

04:57.640 --> 04:59.860
still here, living our lives.

05:00.960 --> 05:05.420
Just be safe,

05:05.910 --> 05:06.980
healthy,

05:08.230 --> 05:10.210
and ordinary.

05:11.150 --> 05:11.890
Can you?

05:12.390 --> 05:13.130
Can you?

05:13.760 --> 05:15.010
Tell me!

05:20.910 --> 05:22.370
I want to be ordinary too.

05:25.790 --> 05:27.370
But there are so many people behind me.

05:29.000 --> 05:30.770
So many who've helped me.

05:32.590 --> 05:33.890
Without Master Qingcheng,

05:35.150 --> 05:36.690
there'd be no Xiaobangchui,

05:38.590 --> 05:40.370
and no Lifei today.

05:42.760 --> 05:43.690
Mr. Zuo Qiu,

05:45.080 --> 05:45.810
Jiaping,

05:46.910 --> 05:47.620
Elder Zhu,

05:49.520 --> 05:51.450
Tongzhou, Gelin,

05:52.030 --> 05:53.620
Ye Ye, Changyue, and so many others.

05:54.640 --> 05:56.130
Everything I've been through seems dangerous,

05:56.910 --> 05:58.500
but it's all gone smoothly.

05:59.710 --> 06:00.370
Master.

06:01.960 --> 06:04.250
People always have my back.

06:05.350 --> 06:07.370
So how could I possibly abandon all of you?

06:15.030 --> 06:15.940
Lifei,

06:16.760 --> 06:18.060
- I... - Master.

06:18.760 --> 06:19.450
Look,

06:19.880 --> 06:21.370
I've got so many people by my side.

06:21.560 --> 06:23.210
I'll be fine, right?

06:24.880 --> 06:25.450
Just

06:26.390 --> 06:28.180
stay at Wuyue Court and heal.

06:28.910 --> 06:29.740
I'll be back

06:30.080 --> 06:32.010
to cook you more good food. Alright?

06:34.350 --> 06:35.660
Qingcheng

06:36.910 --> 06:39.300
said the exact same thing back then.

06:43.200 --> 06:44.060
But in the end...

06:47.710 --> 06:49.330
he never came back.

06:57.120 --> 06:57.980
Master,

06:58.440 --> 07:00.130
you have to have faith in your disciple.

07:00.350 --> 07:00.940
Right?

07:04.390 --> 07:05.060
Let's eat.

07:05.390 --> 07:05.940
Forget it.

07:07.560 --> 07:09.060
It's delicious. Try some.

07:10.880 --> 07:11.770
Try it.

07:13.590 --> 07:14.130
Here.

07:19.320 --> 07:20.500
I found this

07:20.830 --> 07:23.060
at Hushe Peak last time.

07:23.440 --> 07:25.210
If I'm not wrong,

07:26.560 --> 07:28.660
Qingcheng left it for you.

07:29.830 --> 07:31.130
It's a Si beast horn.

07:32.200 --> 07:34.330
Forged from the horn of a Si beast.

07:35.470 --> 07:37.250
It can protect your body and spirit.

07:37.560 --> 07:40.570
With it guarding you,

07:40.910 --> 07:42.690
those who covet your spirit energy

07:43.440 --> 07:45.060
won't have an easy time.

07:46.590 --> 07:47.570
Too bad

07:48.200 --> 07:53.100
Qingcheng never got to hand it to you himself.

07:54.880 --> 07:55.620
Master,

07:57.790 --> 07:59.660
I won't let you all down.

08:00.910 --> 08:01.810
Once this is over,

08:02.790 --> 08:03.660
I'll come back.

08:05.440 --> 08:07.010
I'll be right here waiting for you.

08:24.880 --> 08:26.210
The demons hit the barrier during the day.

08:26.790 --> 08:28.330
Watch out for spies sneaking into the city.

08:28.640 --> 08:29.420
Yes!

09:05.680 --> 09:06.570
Did you do this?

09:08.080 --> 09:09.660
You know how they died?

09:10.630 --> 09:11.570
Besides the ones you killed,

09:12.110 --> 09:13.140
they all died from poison.

09:13.750 --> 09:14.730
There's a rare poison from across the sea

09:15.080 --> 09:15.810
with a faint orchid scent.

09:16.400 --> 09:17.660
Those who take it can't breathe

09:18.160 --> 09:19.020
and suffocate.

09:19.590 --> 09:21.300
As expected of the leader of Jiufeng Clan.

09:22.110 --> 09:23.420
Sharp eyes.

09:23.800 --> 09:25.810
They were just low-level monsters!

09:26.440 --> 09:27.540
Why kill them?

09:28.080 --> 09:30.570
The Sea Calamity is coming. War is almost here.

09:31.040 --> 09:32.850
You monster clan thinks you can stay out of it?

09:33.080 --> 09:33.970
Not a chance.

09:34.990 --> 09:35.780
Mr. Lu,

09:36.440 --> 09:38.260
what if every monster

09:38.280 --> 09:39.570
on Yingcui Island

09:40.160 --> 09:41.570
were poisoned with this?

09:44.040 --> 09:45.180
What exactly do you want?

09:46.350 --> 09:47.380
Simple.

09:47.990 --> 09:51.300
One life for thousands of monsters.

09:53.350 --> 09:54.140
Who do you want to kill?

09:58.160 --> 09:59.420
Mr. Shen.

10:21.110 --> 10:21.780
Lu?

10:24.920 --> 10:25.540
Lu!

10:26.350 --> 10:27.140
I just got back

10:27.160 --> 10:28.730
and heard there was trouble at the barrier again.

10:29.400 --> 10:31.060
The demons are attacking hard this time.

10:32.040 --> 10:32.780
Are you hurt?

10:34.750 --> 10:35.420
I'm fine.

10:36.040 --> 10:36.690
Go back.

10:37.320 --> 10:38.300
You're not fine.

10:38.630 --> 10:39.660
I waited for you all night.

10:40.830 --> 10:42.810
The others said you went out to patrol.

10:43.750 --> 10:44.780
Why did it take so long?

10:45.230 --> 10:46.490
And you went alone. That's so dangerous.

10:54.470 --> 10:57.020
Why do you smell like orchids?

10:57.590 --> 10:58.970
Stay out of my business from now on!

10:59.560 --> 11:00.810
How can I stay out of it?

11:06.080 --> 11:06.690
Gelin.

11:08.040 --> 11:09.380
What are we, really?

11:09.470 --> 11:10.090
We...

11:16.750 --> 11:18.020
What do you think we are?

11:21.350 --> 11:21.900
What,

11:22.440 --> 11:24.140
did you already forget what I said at Wuyue Court?

11:24.470 --> 11:26.090
You said all that for Ye Ye, didn't you?

11:26.560 --> 11:27.090
I...

11:28.750 --> 11:30.210
I'm just something you use to comfort yourself

11:30.230 --> 11:31.210
when you're down.

11:31.990 --> 11:33.540
Don't pretend to care about me.

11:35.990 --> 11:36.660
I don't need it.

11:37.920 --> 11:38.900
What's wrong with you?

11:39.110 --> 11:40.300
What happened?

11:40.400 --> 11:41.180
Baili Gelin!

11:41.800 --> 11:43.490
Don't think every man in the world falls for you.

11:43.920 --> 11:45.090
Go back to Ye Ye.

11:45.350 --> 11:45.810
I...

11:47.280 --> 11:49.380
Get out of the East Sea. You're an eyesore.

11:56.870 --> 11:57.660
You're the eyesore!

11:58.960 --> 12:00.570
Lu Li, you scumbag!

12:15.120 --> 12:15.690
Father.

12:18.160 --> 12:18.780
How did it go?

12:19.310 --> 12:20.740
The list of disciples and their families for evacuation

12:20.760 --> 12:21.450
is ready.

12:21.880 --> 12:23.780
Alright. Have them prepare.

12:23.990 --> 12:25.180
Head inland tomorrow.

12:25.630 --> 12:27.330
Jiao, you go with them.

12:27.760 --> 12:30.130
Father, Duanming City is about to become a battlefield.

12:30.400 --> 12:31.450
I'm staying with you.

12:32.080 --> 12:34.700
If I stay alone, I might survive.

12:34.920 --> 12:37.100
If you stay, we'll both die.

12:38.350 --> 12:38.940
Jiao,

12:39.510 --> 12:40.330
in five hundred years,

12:41.560 --> 12:43.300
you'll be the one fighting on the front lines

12:43.590 --> 12:45.380
and protecting the younger disciples.

12:47.080 --> 12:49.740
Can you take on that burden?

12:51.910 --> 12:52.570
I can.

12:55.360 --> 12:56.250
That's my girl.

12:58.440 --> 12:59.170
That's my girl.

12:59.760 --> 13:02.130
Sir, Lifei and Tongzhou are here.

13:08.680 --> 13:09.970
I couldn't ask earlier.

13:10.400 --> 13:11.570
Is the Fragrance Bond on your palm

13:11.750 --> 13:12.490
gone?

13:31.280 --> 13:32.660
Spare us from mutual slaughter.

13:34.080 --> 13:35.210
Grant me just a little more time,

13:37.680 --> 13:38.450
please.

13:40.920 --> 13:42.090
He and I should've ended this long ago.

13:44.680 --> 13:46.490
I heard about Xiuyuan.

13:48.710 --> 13:50.810
Never thought he'd be the Demon Lord Yecha.

13:57.200 --> 13:58.450
You two still haven't let go?

14:03.560 --> 14:05.330
Maybe your connection runs deeper than this.

14:07.920 --> 14:08.660
Mr. Mo,

14:09.960 --> 14:11.380
he's my enemy now.

14:14.400 --> 14:16.810
Lately, the demons have been hitting the mountain-sea barrier.

14:17.040 --> 14:18.610
But Xiuyuan has never shown himself.

14:19.040 --> 14:19.940
With his power,

14:19.960 --> 14:21.540
the barrier wouldn't stop him.

14:22.470 --> 14:24.020
Maybe he doesn't want to be our enemy.

14:28.510 --> 14:29.570
Even if he doesn't,

14:31.040 --> 14:32.570
who can escape fate?

14:33.320 --> 14:34.850
There's a reason

14:35.160 --> 14:36.380
heaven brought you two together.

14:36.990 --> 14:38.900
When you left the academy,

14:39.080 --> 14:40.610
Mr. Zuo Qiu tested him.

14:41.230 --> 14:42.730
He sensed kindness in him,

14:43.870 --> 14:45.610
so he gave him a chance to enter Wuyue Court.

14:47.400 --> 14:49.690
Maybe Xiuyuan will be our next turning point.

15:00.830 --> 15:01.610
What's that?

15:04.920 --> 15:07.490
Father.

15:07.870 --> 15:08.660
Father!

15:14.470 --> 15:15.570
Phoenix feather?

15:18.680 --> 15:20.610
They say Lu Li is a half-demon,

15:20.870 --> 15:21.850
from the Jiufeng Clan.

15:22.280 --> 15:24.940
Did he kill Mr. Shen?

15:25.400 --> 15:27.090
It's too soon to say that

15:27.560 --> 15:28.260
based on one feather.

15:33.470 --> 15:34.540
Mr. Shen is dead.

15:34.800 --> 15:36.660
Everything's going according to plan.

15:36.710 --> 15:37.660
Too bad.

15:38.280 --> 15:40.690
If they'd just open the mountain-sea barrier,

15:41.040 --> 15:43.540
we could charge into the Central Plains and capture the Divine Tree.

15:44.200 --> 15:46.380
Guardian, Jiang Lifei has come to Duanming City too.

15:46.470 --> 15:48.330
Let's hope she helps the Demon Lord

15:48.920 --> 15:50.090
as she did in the past.

15:50.350 --> 15:51.570
Since Jiang Lifei is here,

15:51.800 --> 15:53.260
I'll sneak back into Duanming City.

15:53.560 --> 15:54.450
I'll kill her

15:54.470 --> 15:55.610
so the Lord can absorb her.

15:57.990 --> 15:59.970
There are many immortals in Duanming City right now.

16:00.400 --> 16:02.450
Ji Tongzhou never leaves Jiang Lifei's side.

16:02.630 --> 16:03.330
It's hard to make a move.

16:03.400 --> 16:04.260
Don't worry.

16:04.990 --> 16:06.300
I have help inside the city.

16:08.200 --> 16:09.610
With your power,

16:10.230 --> 16:12.090
you couldn't have killed Mr. Shen.

16:15.590 --> 16:16.730
Who's the real killer?

16:22.350 --> 16:24.260
Why would a killer leave evidence behind?

16:25.320 --> 16:27.090
Is this a setup to drive us apart?

16:28.110 --> 16:29.970
You don't think Lu Li did it?

16:31.440 --> 16:32.970
We once rescued beasts together.

16:33.590 --> 16:34.780
He helped out

16:34.920 --> 16:35.900
when Duantu was in trouble.

16:36.470 --> 16:37.690
And when I was put on public trial,

16:37.710 --> 16:38.660
he stepped up to help me.

16:39.830 --> 16:40.610
Lu

16:41.110 --> 16:42.090
couldn't be the killer.

16:44.230 --> 16:45.380
But he's from the monster clan.

16:45.710 --> 16:46.610
In a war between immortals and demons,

16:47.110 --> 16:48.570
monsters are caught in the middle.

16:49.110 --> 16:50.090
He might not be bad,

16:50.590 --> 16:52.690
but he could be controlled or used by demons.

16:55.990 --> 16:56.690
Lifei,

16:56.990 --> 16:57.850
the Sea Calamity is coming.

16:58.230 --> 16:59.450
Don't trust others too easily.

17:00.200 --> 17:01.380
But Lu...

17:02.560 --> 17:03.260
What's wrong?

17:04.440 --> 17:05.450
Old injury acting up?

17:05.870 --> 17:06.450
I'm fine.

17:06.960 --> 17:08.250
Just got a little worked up.

17:09.200 --> 17:10.420
You just recovered. Take it easy.

17:11.470 --> 17:12.140
Where's Miaoqing?

17:12.470 --> 17:14.140
With her around, someone can take care of you.

17:15.600 --> 17:16.340
The East Sea is dangerous,

17:16.710 --> 17:17.660
so I didn't bring her.

17:41.640 --> 17:42.970
How's it going?

17:45.600 --> 17:47.900
They've decided Lu Li is the killer.

17:48.640 --> 17:50.580
The immortals and the monster are at odds now.

17:50.960 --> 17:52.450
They'll never work together again.

17:55.200 --> 17:57.450
How many people in the city have you lured

17:57.680 --> 17:58.450
into practicing evil arts?

18:03.990 --> 18:06.290
The Spirit-Devouring Canon is a treasure of the world.

18:06.750 --> 18:08.250
Yet you call it evil arts?

18:09.790 --> 18:10.490
Young man,

18:11.400 --> 18:13.970
without my guidance back then,

18:14.270 --> 18:15.690
you wouldn't be standing here alive.

18:23.360 --> 18:27.180
There's no right or wrong in techniques. Power is the only truth.

18:30.230 --> 18:31.250
Think it over.

18:31.840 --> 18:35.180
You can hand it in or not.

18:39.680 --> 18:40.900
I practice evil arts

18:40.990 --> 18:42.340
to catch demons.

18:42.640 --> 18:43.970
It's for the greater good of the immortal sects.

18:46.750 --> 18:48.100
The greater good?

18:54.680 --> 18:56.290
Then why did you grab that woman?

18:57.470 --> 18:58.660
And you got the wrong one.

19:01.710 --> 19:04.100
Who knew Ji Tongzhou

19:04.360 --> 19:06.860
would disguise a maid as Jiang Lifei?

19:10.750 --> 19:11.820
Since I caught her,

19:12.470 --> 19:13.970
she might be useful.

19:48.470 --> 19:49.140
Don't move!

20:28.790 --> 20:30.100
Lu Li is a half-demon.

20:30.470 --> 20:32.620
Looks like the monsters and demons

20:32.840 --> 20:34.450
are in cahoots.

20:34.640 --> 20:37.450
Truly, those not of our kind can never be trusted.

20:37.920 --> 20:40.620
To kill his own master? How monstrous!

20:41.710 --> 20:42.340
Lu,

20:42.920 --> 20:44.450
did you kill my father?

20:44.880 --> 20:47.490
Jiao, I didn't hurt Master.

20:47.840 --> 20:49.340
I went to him for the antidote!

20:50.120 --> 20:50.900
What antidote?

20:57.880 --> 21:00.900
Qiongqi threatened to kill my people

21:01.440 --> 21:02.420
if I didn't harm Master.

21:02.960 --> 21:04.210
I told Master this.

21:04.710 --> 21:05.820
He gave me the antidote

21:06.270 --> 21:07.770
and told me to leave Duanming City immediately.

21:08.360 --> 21:09.010
I refused,

21:09.440 --> 21:10.420
and we argued.

21:11.120 --> 21:12.450
Later, on my way back from Yingcui Island,

21:12.790 --> 21:14.620
Qiongqi ambushed me, wounded me badly,

21:15.070 --> 21:16.050
and forced me to reveal my true form.

21:19.160 --> 21:19.970
I only learned

21:20.990 --> 21:22.450
of Master's death after I returned.

21:24.120 --> 21:25.580
Mr. Shen is dead.

21:25.920 --> 21:26.940
You can say whatever you want.

21:27.640 --> 21:28.620
You're from the monster clan

21:29.680 --> 21:31.250
and the chief disciple of Wanxian Sect.

21:31.960 --> 21:33.900
You know how to open the mountain-sea barrier.

21:34.230 --> 21:35.690
Keeping him in Duanming City

21:35.920 --> 21:36.860
is a huge risk

21:36.960 --> 21:38.180
to the immortal sects

21:38.440 --> 21:39.690
and the Central Plains.

21:41.310 --> 21:42.180
I say

21:42.750 --> 21:44.290
we execute this monster now

21:44.840 --> 21:46.490
to honor Mr. Shen's spirit

21:46.790 --> 21:48.010
and remove the threat forever.

21:57.400 --> 21:58.530
Mr. Luo, the truth isn't clear yet.

21:59.270 --> 22:00.450
You're in such a hurry to move.

22:00.880 --> 22:01.820
Are you trying to silence him?

22:02.230 --> 22:02.940
Jiang Lifei,

22:03.920 --> 22:05.860
you're the real source of all this trouble.

22:06.680 --> 22:08.290
You arrived in Duanming City not long ago,

22:08.310 --> 22:09.530
and Mr. Shen was killed.

22:10.510 --> 22:14.100
Have you outcasts been secretly scheming together

22:14.400 --> 22:15.450
all along?

22:16.440 --> 22:17.860
This has nothing to do with Lifei.

22:18.400 --> 22:19.900
Mr. Luo, why are you making false accusations?

22:20.360 --> 22:21.770
Am I making false accusations,

22:22.310 --> 22:24.420
or is this wretch hiding evil intent?

22:24.880 --> 22:26.620
Duanming City is in this mess

22:27.030 --> 22:29.010
because you've been shielding her.

22:29.750 --> 22:31.180
When the monsters last caused trouble,

22:31.270 --> 22:32.660
it was Immortal Cuixuan

22:32.680 --> 22:33.970
and Mr. Shen who held the line

22:34.230 --> 22:35.620
and saved Duanming City.

22:36.230 --> 22:37.380
Now, not even a year later,

22:37.750 --> 22:39.050
Mr. Shen is dead.

22:39.360 --> 22:41.860
And Immortal Cuixuan has been framed!

22:42.680 --> 22:43.900
Cuixuan slaughtered innocents.

22:44.510 --> 22:45.690
He got what he deserved.

22:46.030 --> 22:47.420
That's just your one-sided story!

22:47.960 --> 22:48.490
Jiang Lifei,

22:48.960 --> 22:50.450
you're just an outcast from across the sea.

22:50.840 --> 22:53.450
Immortal Cuixuan led the sect for centuries.

22:53.880 --> 22:55.860
He protected the people and stood for the righteous path.

22:56.200 --> 22:57.380
Even if he made mistakes,

22:57.510 --> 22:58.940
it was for the greater good!

22:59.310 --> 23:00.210
What greater good?

23:03.270 --> 23:05.010
We're talking about Mr. Shen's death.

23:05.640 --> 23:07.580
Why are you defending that villain Cuixuan?

23:07.990 --> 23:08.290
You!

23:13.920 --> 23:15.210
I'm speaking the truth.

23:17.070 --> 23:19.730
There's solid evidence that Lu Li killed Mr. Shen.

23:20.160 --> 23:21.900
Yet you defend him.

23:21.960 --> 23:22.860
What are you really after?

23:23.440 --> 23:27.180
Hasn't Duanming City suffered enough?

23:27.400 --> 23:28.050
Luo Chengji!

23:28.920 --> 23:30.380
If you keep targeting Lifei, don't blame me...

23:30.400 --> 23:31.010
Enough!

23:32.440 --> 23:33.180
Stop.

23:36.680 --> 23:38.580
My father once said that all beings are equal.

23:39.400 --> 23:40.490
We should not judge

23:40.920 --> 23:42.340
monsters or beasts by prejudice.

23:43.160 --> 23:44.490
He knew Lu Li's identity

23:45.070 --> 23:46.250
when he took him in.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.660
He taught Lu for over a decade

23:48.680 --> 23:49.660
and saw him as a son.

23:50.160 --> 23:51.210
I trust my father,

23:51.840 --> 23:53.290
and I trust Lu.

23:54.030 --> 23:54.620
Jiao.

23:54.960 --> 23:55.490
Jiao,

23:55.920 --> 23:58.940
your father's kindness is what got him killed.

23:59.120 --> 24:00.100
This monster must be eliminated!

24:00.400 --> 24:01.140
Mr. Luo,

24:01.680 --> 24:02.970
this is Wanxian Sect's territory.

24:03.550 --> 24:05.290
I'm the sect leader now.

24:05.550 --> 24:06.660
I'll decide

24:07.070 --> 24:08.620
how to handle this.

24:09.600 --> 24:11.580
Someone! Take Lu Li into custody for now.

24:11.840 --> 24:12.340
- Yes! - Yes!

24:23.640 --> 24:24.180
Get lost!

24:25.750 --> 24:26.250
My Lord.

24:26.840 --> 24:28.250
You acted on your own

24:28.470 --> 24:29.340
while I was unconscious.

24:30.230 --> 24:31.730
Do you have any respect for me?

24:32.400 --> 24:34.620
Qiongqi killed Mr. Shen for you.

24:35.550 --> 24:36.970
The curse is acting up more and more often.

24:36.990 --> 24:38.050
If you don't absorb the Divine Tree,

24:38.070 --> 24:39.730
you'll die, My Lord!

24:40.680 --> 24:41.770
Is this about the Divine Tree,

24:42.710 --> 24:44.180
or forcing my hand?

24:45.030 --> 24:46.180
With Mr. Shen dead,

24:46.440 --> 24:47.490
the two clans will be at each other's throats.

24:48.270 --> 24:49.620
You're just asking for war!

24:52.550 --> 24:53.100
Yes!

24:54.070 --> 24:55.490
The Sea Calamity is almost here.

24:56.470 --> 24:58.420
We've waited for five hundred years.

24:58.640 --> 25:00.180
Everything comes down to this!

25:02.920 --> 25:03.900
I don't want war.

25:04.550 --> 25:05.290
Not because I fear it,

25:06.030 --> 25:07.580
but because I don't want our people to die in vain!

25:11.270 --> 25:11.730
My Lord.

25:12.310 --> 25:12.820
My Lord!

25:13.120 --> 25:14.180
- Your body... - Don't follow me!

25:16.360 --> 25:17.820
My Lord!

25:20.360 --> 25:21.290
My Lord!

25:32.400 --> 25:32.970
Lu.

25:34.470 --> 25:35.010
Why are you here?

25:37.310 --> 25:38.660
Jiao asked me to give this to you.

25:44.600 --> 25:45.530
I didn't kill Master.

25:53.160 --> 25:53.860
I know.

26:02.400 --> 26:04.010
Jiao sent this hairpin

26:05.120 --> 26:05.900
to help you escape.

26:12.640 --> 26:13.140
Escape?

26:15.120 --> 26:16.860
The killer set you up. This doesn't look good for you.

26:18.120 --> 26:19.770
Jiao said you should leave the city immediately.

26:20.230 --> 26:21.010
If I leave,

26:21.270 --> 26:22.940
I'm admitting I killed Master.

26:23.990 --> 26:24.580
I can't leave.

26:26.960 --> 26:28.100
Staying here won't clear your name.

26:28.400 --> 26:29.340
I have to stay!

26:30.310 --> 26:31.100
Whoever did this

26:31.400 --> 26:32.660
isn't just trying to split Wanxian Sect.

26:33.310 --> 26:33.970
They're trying to stir up hatred

26:33.990 --> 26:35.380
between humans and monsters.

26:35.880 --> 26:36.730
If I leave,

26:36.960 --> 26:38.250
Jiao will be blamed by the immortal sects.

26:38.840 --> 26:40.580
And the monsters in the East Sea will be leaderless.

26:41.710 --> 26:42.820
Everyone knows you're a monster.

26:44.270 --> 26:44.860
If you stay,

26:44.880 --> 26:45.940
they won't let you go!

26:47.990 --> 26:48.770
Just because I'm a monster,

26:49.160 --> 26:50.730
I can't stay in Duanming City?

26:51.120 --> 26:52.690
I don't care if you're human or a monster.

26:55.990 --> 26:57.140
But those immortals out there

26:57.160 --> 26:58.340
don't think that way.

26:59.790 --> 27:00.770
Prejudice is a weapon.

27:01.440 --> 27:02.900
Have you forgotten what happened to Lifei?

27:05.440 --> 27:06.940
Lu, just go.

27:14.230 --> 27:14.660
Gelin.

27:16.070 --> 27:16.580
I'm sorry.

27:21.440 --> 27:22.490
Lu, what are you doing?

27:46.710 --> 27:48.940
Gelin, the blood bond is broken.

27:51.790 --> 27:52.380
You're free now.

27:58.070 --> 27:58.820
Lu,

28:00.790 --> 28:01.770
are you abandoning me?

28:12.680 --> 28:13.420
You're right.

28:14.960 --> 28:15.770
Prejudice hurts.

28:16.790 --> 28:18.420
You shouldn't be tied to a monster like me.

28:19.510 --> 28:21.290
Go inland with Mr. Mo

28:22.030 --> 28:22.820
and return to Chufeng Academy.

28:39.920 --> 28:41.290
You said we should be together.

28:42.200 --> 28:43.660
Now you say we're breaking up.

28:44.960 --> 28:46.180
You get to decide everything?

28:46.790 --> 28:47.900
What do I even mean to you?

28:53.600 --> 28:54.900
You always have your reasons.

28:56.470 --> 28:57.820
You change your mind so easily.

28:58.750 --> 29:00.050
You abandon me so easily.

29:01.160 --> 29:02.290
None of you keep your word.

29:05.440 --> 29:06.620
You all say it's for my own good

29:07.230 --> 29:08.210
and send me away.

29:10.640 --> 29:11.820
But where am I supposed to go?

29:13.070 --> 29:14.450
What do you want me to do?

29:17.440 --> 29:19.250
Didn't you always want to take this necklace off?

29:21.270 --> 29:22.450
You don't understand anything!

29:28.550 --> 29:29.050
Gelin.

29:31.070 --> 29:32.140
Let Lu stay.

29:46.960 --> 29:49.380
They killed Mr. Shen and framed Lu.

29:49.640 --> 29:50.820
There must be more to this.

30:00.920 --> 30:01.940
Lifei, Yanfan,

30:02.550 --> 30:03.860
let's go check the mountain-sea barrier.

30:23.990 --> 30:24.530
Stop!

30:40.070 --> 30:41.100
Verbal command spell?

30:51.030 --> 30:52.100
Zhenyunzi?

30:52.750 --> 30:53.490
So it's you.

30:55.960 --> 30:56.770
Xiaobangchui.

30:57.070 --> 30:57.860
Jiang Lifei.

30:58.270 --> 30:59.580
Long time no see.

31:00.200 --> 31:01.860
Trouble never dies.

31:02.030 --> 31:02.940
You're still alive.

31:06.470 --> 31:07.580
You're still alive.

31:07.880 --> 31:09.140
How could I die?

31:09.310 --> 31:10.620
If I'd known you were the Divine Tree,

31:10.640 --> 31:12.100
I wouldn't have hunted the Nine-Tailed Fox.

31:14.470 --> 31:15.380
You're all I need!

31:32.270 --> 31:33.490
The Spirit-Devouring Art?

31:34.160 --> 31:35.180
You've sided with demons too?

31:36.030 --> 31:37.340
Thanks to you and Lei Xiuyuan!

31:37.880 --> 31:39.010
I'm just returning the favor!

32:02.550 --> 32:03.290
Miaoqing?

32:05.710 --> 32:06.770
You've actually improved

32:07.030 --> 32:08.420
over these few years.

32:08.750 --> 32:10.290
But still too green!

32:28.710 --> 32:29.210
Lifei.

32:30.400 --> 32:30.970
Are you okay?

32:36.920 --> 32:37.900
Mr. Zhenyun?

32:39.960 --> 32:41.210
After all these years,

32:41.640 --> 32:43.450
you're now colluding with demons

32:44.120 --> 32:45.210
against the immortal sects?

32:46.470 --> 32:47.250
Ji Tongzhou,

32:47.790 --> 32:49.010
you useless kid.

32:49.360 --> 32:50.820
Xingzheng Hall was wiped out.

32:50.840 --> 32:51.690
The Yue State was destroyed.

32:52.070 --> 32:53.100
You can't tell what matters.

32:53.440 --> 32:54.450
You're not using the Divine Tree!

32:54.990 --> 32:56.490
You think owning the Divine Tree

32:56.750 --> 32:59.050
makes you the ruler of the immortal sects?

32:59.960 --> 33:02.900
The Divine Tree's heart belongs to Lei Xiuyuan.

33:03.160 --> 33:04.290
It was never yours!

33:04.310 --> 33:04.900
Shut up!

33:07.880 --> 33:09.940
You've mastered Xuanhua Sacred Fire?

33:19.880 --> 33:20.450
Take care of her.

33:21.160 --> 33:21.730
Lifei!

33:25.960 --> 33:26.340
Lifei!

33:27.400 --> 33:28.290
He has backup?

33:35.960 --> 33:37.530
Miaoqing.

33:38.880 --> 33:39.450
Are you okay?

33:44.440 --> 33:45.420
I'm fine.

33:46.600 --> 33:47.380
It's my fault.

33:48.550 --> 33:50.420
I've caused you trouble, Your Highness.

33:53.120 --> 33:54.420
Miaoqing. Miaoqing!

33:56.310 --> 33:56.900
Miaoqing.

34:09.310 --> 34:09.820
Qiongqi.

34:10.550 --> 34:11.620
Why didn't you strike sooner?

34:11.790 --> 34:12.650
The Divine Tree got away again!

34:18.030 --> 34:19.050
Lei Xiuyuan?

34:30.320 --> 34:30.970
Demon Lord.

34:31.470 --> 34:32.820
I've pledged myself to the demons.

34:33.800 --> 34:34.780
We had some misunderstandings.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.530
Please be magnanimous.

34:39.400 --> 34:39.940
Misunderstandings?

34:41.320 --> 34:42.450
To help Mr. Qiongqi,

34:43.190 --> 34:44.340
I killed Mr. Shen.

34:44.840 --> 34:46.820
And I've planted pawns throughout Duanming City,

34:47.400 --> 34:48.450
training them in demonic arts

34:48.470 --> 34:49.220
for you.

34:50.150 --> 34:51.010
You can ask Mr. Qiongqi

34:51.190 --> 34:53.650
about my loyalty.

34:58.070 --> 34:59.170
Your spirit root was destroyed.

35:00.590 --> 35:02.530
Even with the Spirit-Devouring Canon,

35:03.240 --> 35:04.820
you couldn't have killed Mr. Shen.

35:10.840 --> 35:11.970
Who's really

35:14.150 --> 35:15.170
behind you?

35:16.800 --> 35:17.780
What do you mean?

35:19.470 --> 35:21.740
I've known Mr. Shen for years.

35:21.990 --> 35:23.130
He never suspected me.

35:23.150 --> 35:24.260
One strike was all it took.

35:27.630 --> 35:28.740
You're a born rebel.

35:29.840 --> 35:31.570
You'd never truly serve Qiongqi.

35:33.110 --> 35:34.610
Not a demon.

35:35.510 --> 35:38.300
Yet powerful enough to match Mr. Shen.

35:43.280 --> 35:44.300
That means he is...

35:44.590 --> 35:45.700
I killed Mr. Shen!

35:48.360 --> 35:49.610
If I weren't so soft-hearted,

35:50.070 --> 35:51.940
I'd have devoured that old fool's spirit energy!

36:05.800 --> 36:06.450
Lei Xiuyuan!

36:07.030 --> 36:08.530
I should've killed you back then.

36:09.470 --> 36:10.650
What would Lu Shanhua think

36:11.400 --> 36:13.380
if he knew the one he died protecting

36:14.240 --> 36:15.340
is a demon?

36:16.670 --> 36:18.340
You don't deserve to say his name.

36:18.880 --> 36:20.340
Lu Shanhua was worthless!

36:34.800 --> 36:36.340
For all the pain Lu suffered,

36:37.030 --> 36:38.700
I'll make you pay a thousand times over!

36:38.990 --> 36:40.260
Use your technique

36:40.280 --> 36:41.820
to kill this demon!

36:47.800 --> 36:49.170
I am the Demon Lord Yecha.

36:50.440 --> 36:53.570
All demonic energy answers to me.

36:54.360 --> 36:55.900
You're using it against me?

37:12.510 --> 37:13.130
Lu,

37:14.990 --> 37:15.740
you can

37:17.840 --> 37:18.700
rest in peace now.

37:38.240 --> 37:38.780
Miaoqing.

37:39.360 --> 37:40.170
Are you feeling better?

37:42.280 --> 37:45.130
Miss Jiang, you're healing me again.

37:46.190 --> 37:47.450
I don't deserve this.

37:48.630 --> 37:49.450
You're still weak.

37:49.920 --> 37:50.780
Lie down.

37:52.510 --> 37:53.260
Lie down.

37:57.360 --> 37:59.090
Good thing Zhenyunzi didn't torture you.

37:59.670 --> 38:00.380
You're not badly hurt.

38:01.110 --> 38:04.130
They wanted to use me to pressure His Highness.

38:05.030 --> 38:06.380
They were after you, Miss Jiang,

38:06.960 --> 38:08.380
so they didn't hurt me much.

38:09.990 --> 38:12.860
I never expected that snake Zhenyunzi

38:12.880 --> 38:13.940
to practice demonic arts too.

38:15.440 --> 38:16.340
We don't know

38:16.670 --> 38:18.090
how many more in the city are doing the same.

38:18.760 --> 38:20.340
With all the sects in panic,

38:20.920 --> 38:21.700
it'll be hard

38:21.920 --> 38:22.860
to find out anytime soon.

38:24.400 --> 38:24.940
Miaoqing,

38:25.720 --> 38:26.940
did Zhenyunzi

38:27.150 --> 38:28.300
have any accomplices?

38:30.190 --> 38:30.700
I...

38:31.320 --> 38:32.340
I didn't see anyone.

38:33.280 --> 38:35.090
But I did hear a voice.

38:35.670 --> 38:36.450
Very rude.

38:36.720 --> 38:37.650
Something like

38:38.470 --> 38:39.860
"The Lord urgently needs the Divine Tree."

38:40.190 --> 38:41.940
"Tell Zhenyunzi to hurry."

38:42.470 --> 38:43.170
The Lord?

38:48.190 --> 38:50.450
Only demons call the Demon Lord like that.

38:51.360 --> 38:51.820
So

38:52.030 --> 38:53.260
Zhenyunzi was taking orders from Lei...

38:56.800 --> 38:57.820
I mean, from that demon scum.

39:02.070 --> 39:03.170
It's getting more dangerous here.

39:03.800 --> 39:04.300
Miaoqing,

39:04.840 --> 39:05.700
you should go inland

39:05.720 --> 39:06.570
with Mr. Mo and the others.

39:07.190 --> 39:07.700
No.

39:08.550 --> 39:09.570
I'm not going anywhere.

39:10.510 --> 39:11.340
I won't leave.

39:12.030 --> 39:12.780
Miss Jiang,

39:13.670 --> 39:15.170
please don't send me away.

39:15.920 --> 39:16.700
Don't misunderstand.

39:16.920 --> 39:17.700
I'm not sending you away.

39:18.670 --> 39:19.940
It really is getting dangerous here.

39:20.800 --> 39:22.130
I don't want you caught up in this.

39:22.720 --> 39:23.420
I'll be fine.

39:23.840 --> 39:25.610
I won't be a burden to His Highness or you.

39:26.400 --> 39:27.740
I'll be really careful

39:28.280 --> 39:29.380
and won't let them catch me.

39:31.720 --> 39:32.170
Your Highness,

39:32.800 --> 39:34.130
please don't send me away.

39:38.240 --> 39:38.860
You can stay.

39:40.440 --> 39:41.050
She's injured.

39:41.360 --> 39:42.820
The road back to Duantu is long

39:43.030 --> 39:43.780
and dangerous.

39:44.760 --> 39:45.530
Thank you, Your Highness.

39:55.880 --> 39:57.780
Two lovers on opposite shores.

39:58.510 --> 40:00.340
An inch apart yet worlds away.

40:02.840 --> 40:05.940
Is this fate or a curse?

40:17.400 --> 40:18.260
Why didn't you dodge?

40:19.360 --> 40:20.380
Once I've fulfilled my purpose,

40:21.800 --> 40:22.970
my life is yours.

40:28.840 --> 40:29.900
Did you order

40:30.440 --> 40:31.530
Mr. Shen's death?

40:32.030 --> 40:32.650
No.

40:36.630 --> 40:37.570
Then why are you here?

40:38.360 --> 40:39.380
To stir more trouble in Duanming City?

40:41.960 --> 40:43.220
I'm here to take my subordinates back.

40:43.630 --> 40:44.300
Subordinates?

40:46.320 --> 40:47.380
Qiongqi or Rakshasa?

40:48.590 --> 40:49.530
They're working with Zhenyunzi.

40:49.550 --> 40:50.300
Did you know?

40:52.110 --> 40:53.260
I've already killed Zhenyunzi

40:54.150 --> 40:55.050
to avenge Lu.

40:57.630 --> 40:59.650
He was practicing Spirit-Devouring Canon.

41:00.590 --> 41:02.090
How many more in the city are doing the same?

41:04.630 --> 41:05.220
I don't know.

41:06.920 --> 41:08.220
But I can help you find out.

41:09.360 --> 41:09.860
Lifei!

41:12.960 --> 41:13.420
Tongzhou.

41:14.990 --> 41:15.530
Lifei,

41:16.070 --> 41:17.050
what are you doing out here?

41:18.670 --> 41:20.530
I heard from Wanxian Sect disciples

41:21.030 --> 41:22.050
that this path leads outside the city.

41:22.240 --> 41:23.010
So I came to check.

41:24.280 --> 41:26.300
Let the disciples handle these things.

41:26.630 --> 41:27.610
It's getting dark.

41:27.630 --> 41:28.740
What if someone ambushed you?

41:29.150 --> 41:30.740
You called me paranoid before.

41:31.400 --> 41:32.860
Now you're worse than me.

41:33.360 --> 41:34.260
I'm not being paranoid.

41:34.630 --> 41:35.740
But Miaoqing

41:35.960 --> 41:37.740
was taken without a sound.

41:38.070 --> 41:39.380
I'm terrified you might be taken too.

41:47.550 --> 41:48.610
I just needed some air.

41:49.190 --> 41:50.050
Look.

41:50.550 --> 41:52.260
I was practicing the Si beast horn blade my master gave me.

41:53.030 --> 41:54.050
All done now.

41:54.070 --> 41:54.450
Let's go.

41:57.880 --> 41:58.450
It's been a long day.

41:58.470 --> 41:59.170
I'm exhausted.

42:00.760 --> 42:01.260
Okay.

42:01.400 --> 42:02.130
Let's go rest.

42:02.720 --> 42:03.130
Let's go.

42:14.720 --> 42:15.220
Now, tell me.

42:16.400 --> 42:18.130
How many more are practicing the secret canon?

42:19.360 --> 42:21.650
How did Mr. Shen really die?

42:22.150 --> 42:23.050
My Lord, don't trouble yourself.

42:23.550 --> 42:24.970
I've already set everything in place in the city.

42:25.630 --> 42:27.170
This time, I'll strike them hard.

42:27.990 --> 42:28.610
Stop.

42:29.630 --> 42:30.220
Go back.

42:30.360 --> 42:32.450
I've been preparing for this battle for five hundred years!

42:32.920 --> 42:33.940
I can't let it all fall apart now!

42:36.990 --> 42:38.220
You dare defy me?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
